How to use FontAwesome in React

1. Install
  $ npm i --save @fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core
  $ npm i --save @fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons
  $ npm i --save @fortawesome/react-fontawesome
  
2. Import into your component
  import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome';
  import { faThumbsUp } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons';

3. Use
  <FontAwesomeIcon icon={ faThumbsUp } size="lg"/>


How to install axios

1. $ npm i axios
2. import axios from "axios";
(to the component you're gonna use it on)


How to install bootstrap

1. $ npm i bootstrap@4.3.1
2. import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css";
(to Index.js)


How to install GoogleFonts

@import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Darker+Grotesque&display=swap");
(update url to font you will use)
